Class Aircraft

java.lang.Object
Inheritance.Transportation
Inheritance.Aircraft
Direct Known Subclasses:
Airplane
public class Aircraft extends Transportation
The Aircraft class is a subclass of Transportation. The Aircraft class describes a transportation method that is capable of flight, with propertities such as altitute. The Aircraft class is intented to extend into specific types of aircrafts, such as airplanes.
